## 🚀 Quick Start (15 Minutes)

### Step 1: Get API Key (2 min)
```
1. Visit https://aistudio.google.com
2. Click "Get API key"
3. Select "Create API key in new project"
4. Copy your API key
```

### Step 2: Configure App (1 min)
```
1. Open mubra-chemistry-app.html in text editor
2. Find line: GEMINI_API_KEY: 'YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE'
3. Replace with your actual key
4. Save file (Ctrl+S)
```

### Step 3: Test Locally (5 min)
```
1. Double-click mubra-chemistry-app.html
2. App opens in browser
3. Type a chemistry question
4. Get AI response
5. ✅ Everything works!
```

### Step 4: Deploy (5 min)
```
1. Create GitHub repository
2. Upload HTML file
3. Enable GitHub Pages
4. Your app is live!
```

