## 🔧 Customization Guide

### Change Colors
Edit `:root` CSS variables (line ~100):
```css
--navy-primary: #001F3F;
--gold-primary: #D4AF37;
/* Change any color codes */
```

### Change AI Personality
Edit `SYSTEM_INSTRUCTION` (line ~610):
```javascript
const SYSTEM_INSTRUCTION = `Your custom prompt in Sinhala`;
```

### Add New Lessons
Duplicate sidebar item and update:
```html
<div class="sidebar-item" data-lesson="analytical">
    <span>🔍</span> Analytical Chemistry
</div>
```

### Modify Layout
Edit CSS media queries (line ~350-450) for responsive behavior

